ly model-independent test of the Etherington distance\nduality relation between redshifts of $0.38$ and $0.61$. We find consistency\nwith the standard distance duality relation and constrain the optical depth of\nlight between these two redshifts to $\\Delta\\tau=-0.006\\pm0.046$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Dec 2016 01:28:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-30"}
