 outperforms the\nstate-of-the-art superpixel algorithms in accuracy and presents a competitive\nperformance in computational efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Dec 2016 02:58:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2017 02:28:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-22"}
