er in the telescope aperture allows us\nto obtain the angular and energy resolutions better in this range than in\ncurrent space missions. The gamma-ray telescope angular resolution at 50-MeV\ngamma rays is better than 5 deg and energy resolution is ~10%. We report the\nmethod providing these results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Dec 2016 13:21:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-30"}
